title: List DAI as Collateral Asset
body:
## Summary

List DAI as Collateral Assset

**For**: List DAI as collateral asset
**Against**: Do nothing

## Motivation

DAI, as a major coin and also a stable coin, would bring a great amount of TVL to the protocol. We believe it would benefits the protocol with its high circulation, and we can earn reserve from it.
author: 0xb6e362900B7113F246A7e1c17E9746b3B9C079dB
